{"tid":670163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：鬈毛男　機場演脫衣騷","createTime":"2018-05-19T06:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T07:25:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49abc5a23b4bf43015a78b0eed360be4454ef7ae","tid":670163,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395413&d=JR2usU%2BT2p6nOzQaRXHyQxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3aa8bbb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395413&h=bbbb776c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395413</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：鬈毛男　機場演脫衣騷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180519/large/a1504a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180519%2Flarge%2Fa1504a.gif&h=98241159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■機場職員發現光豬男後即時向上級報告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢排日日都天口㷫，但機場冷氣充足，絕對同個熱字扯唔上關係。之但係讀者鄭先生，前日（17日）喺機場禁區入面，就見到位仁兄光脫脫咁，真係巧驚驚呀，搞咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n鄭先生前日黃昏6點左右，喺一號客運大樓離港層環亞機場貴賓室行出來，見到一位鬈毛嘅男士喺玻璃窗旁邊，放低背包之後就開始除衫至光脫脫，呢位男士嘅朋友仲喺一邊食花生，完全冇阻止。由於佢嘅行為太出位，即刻俾機場職員發現，仲喺對講機向上級報告。<br />\n<br />\n鄭生估計呢位裸男玩緊行為藝術，藝術嘅嘢，小記識條鐵咩！只知道佢喺公眾場合剝光豬係犯法箒。機管局發言人話，事發後已即刻報警，而警方證實，當日帶走咗一位26歲非華裔男子，並將佢送去北大嶼山醫院，案列發現懷疑精神混亂人士處理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：肥叔浸浴　公園水池變「太子」桑拿<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：巴士垃圾蟲神邏輯　「有人清潔 你唔知呀？」"},{"pid":"414206ad44f50df9cd2300a5b83a04ade10c1eb3","tid":670163,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"發現傻人案"},{"pid":"ca5f1cb83853e0134d2266d2ee32639872d736b1","tid":670163,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19b7db10b8504fbdb9bcd1f03f201635dbbbb01f","tid":670163,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca5f1cb83853e0134d2266d2ee32639872d736b1","tid":670163,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"哈比人"}]}